{"tid":741192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80歲阿伯沙田偷自由行篋 連560蚊藥油都唔放過","createTime":"2018-07-13T12:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T13:06:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5c8c3b12842d2c0c5b831898f2fbd4dff0d2aa","tid":741192,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:56:42.000Z","msg":"中午12時許，沙田分區特遣隊在沙田一帶進行反罪惡巡邏，期間警員發現一名80歲男子形跡可疑，遂上前截查他，經初步調查。相信他涉嫌與6月至7月期間在新城市廣場的3宗盜竊案有關，共盜去3名內地遊客兩個行李箱及一架手推車；其中一個行李箱內有3隻手錶、化妝品及健康食品，總值約8,000元；另一行李箱內有約值2,000元的化妝品；手推車內有約1,200元現金、一部約值7,000元的手提電話、兩罐共約值700元的奶粉及6支共約值560元的藥油。被捕男子現正被扣留調查，案件交由沙田警區刑事調查隊第七隊跟進。"},{"pid":"82fea8f1b79b16fd462b892a2b0a094a3115df77","tid":741192,"uid":48076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5d4ae641ac80110c6a9b11cb26f19da21628b8","tid":741192,"uid":81340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"終於搵到用處<br />\n7~80都唔會坐好耐<br />\n又有皇家飯食<br />\n一舉兩得"},{"pid":"da9d07352f1896281c76ec9db412c8068f8c49e7","tid":741192,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5d4ae641ac80110c6a9b11cb26f19da21628b8","tid":741192,"uid":81340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"終於搵到用處<br />\n7~80都唔會坐好耐<br />\n又有皇家飯食<br />\n一舉兩得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"依家仲邊有皇家飯食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5e5f724252cdefada12539b6bc07eff04dac91","tid":741192,"uid":166663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"廢老﹐80歲都唔撚化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba198b120c3dc873f61905136c492d283904524","tid":741192,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da9d07352f1896281c76ec9db412c8068f8c49e7","tid":741192,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,